    "description": "In this action-packed adventure, you will harness incredible powers to save the city from the clutches of the militia. With flight, super speed, heat vision, super strength, and x-ray vision at your disposal, you are the only one capable of taking down the enemy bases and rescuing innocent civilians.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258330/extras/4eb16c1f2bebdfe4515fb36a9be4c397.poster.avif?t=1738084080\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258330/extras/4eb16c1f2bebdfe4515fb36a9be4c397.webm?t=1738084080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258330/extras/4eb16c1f2bebdfe4515fb36a9be4c397.mp4?t=1738084080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore a vast open-world city, filled with exciting events and challenges around every corner. Keep an eye out for distress signals and respond quickly to save the day. Use your powers strategically to overcome obstacles and defeat the toughest enemies.<br><br>Team up with other players to take on the most challenging missions and fight together against the militia. Coordinate your powers to achieve victory and become the ultimate superhero team.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258330/extras/61fa78c57ef446ca3d70bb921251c035.poster.avif?t=1738084080\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258330/extras/61fa78c57ef446ca3d70bb921251c035.webm?t=1738084080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258330/extras/61fa78c57ef446ca3d70bb921251c035.mp4?t=1738084080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>With stunning graphics and epic battles, this game will transport you to a world where anything is possible. Soar through the sky, race through the streets, and unleash your full potential as a superhero. Are you ready to save the city and become Valorous? The fate of the city is in your hands!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258330/extras/faf3636fe93951d55d754a5bf85f47a5.poster.avif?t=1738084080\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258330/extras/faf3636fe93951d55d754a5bf85f47a5.webm?t=1738084080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258330/extras/faf3636fe93951d55d754a5bf85f47a5.mp4?t=1738084080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
